Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A racing second hand,\Na glittering shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan's logic is good medicine for\Nhearts dried by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.41,0:00:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's stage is a giant mansion!\NMy rival Heiji also plays a big role!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid but\Nhas the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Case of the Eminent Family's\NStrange Deaths, Part 1."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:02:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an elegant mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect nothing less from\Nthe head of the Nagato Group,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which stands equal with Sonoko's family!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know Miss Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She visited a few times\Nwhen she was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Miss" doesn't quite fit her, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does someone that\Nimportant want to see you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He personally asked for\Nthe great Mori Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants me to solve a big case!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or make sure his wife isn't cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these holes around the pond?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We plan to plant new trees\Nhere by the week's end...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my lateness,\Nbut I am Take Kuranosuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the family's butler for\Nthe last two generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! The inside is amazing, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The master waits on the third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are lots of guards...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally. It's a big case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Haven't I seen him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Find your first love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?! The great Mori Kogoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:24.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato Dosan (60) President of Nagato Group
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My old friend assured me you could...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...find her with lightning speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't need to bring\Nme here just to ask that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad it wasn't a big case, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any photos of this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We met during grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even remember her face...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, for some reason,\NI'm reminded of how lovely she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My late wife may not be\Nhappy to hear that, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no photographs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I do know her name\Nand her later whereabouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them, Hyuga-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:10.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyuga Miyuki (26) Mr. Nagato's Secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Akagi Kotomi,\Nfrom Kanagawa Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After graduation,\Nshe married at age 29.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She and husband Yamato\NKohei had one child,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but all three suddenly\Ndisappeared five years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure they didn't flee by night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unthinkable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this old friend who\Nrecommended me, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the old friend I mentioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osaka's Chief of Police,\NHattori Heizo-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osaka's Chief of Police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's always on TV whenever\Nsomething happens in Osaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he looked familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Does that mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Kudo! How ya been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori Heiji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? They still don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By "Kudo," do you mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Kuro"! As in\N"thanks for your hard work"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you have company, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:19.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato Nobuko (39), Eldest Daughter\NNagato Yasue (32), Second Daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not just guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A vixen is here, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told you've been\Nstaying here recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What scheme are you cooking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Nobuko!\NI am unable to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need her to send notes to the office...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fax machine could do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not that simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detectives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are detectives here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He called them here to ask\Nthem to find his first--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody asked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have that filthy pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it's your\Ndad's keepsake! It's creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better watch out, or she'll\Nsteal your Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0}, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such rudeness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, Hyuga-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's simply upset that\Nshe hasn't found a man yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt she'll ever find one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I should return to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hyuga-{\i1}kun{\i0}. I'd like to\Nmake the announcement tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so if you do pity my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't pity him at all!\NThis is our fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A "bond of flames" has connected\Nus for a long time now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bond of flames"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two were in the same kendo club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Nagato-{\i1}san {\i0}used to\Nbeat me down like a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, Heizo. About the matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I had the guards\Ndouble-check, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son, Hideomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His face was burned
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in an accident long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:24.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato Hideomi (36) Eldest Son & Novelist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think modern plastic\Nsurgery could fix most of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's against the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's a happy ending,\Nall thanks to the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Hideomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hideomi! Wait!\NWhat're you so mad for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you a happy birthday, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:08:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate it if you'd give me\Nthe title of president in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be getting back to Osaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're not going to\Ncelebrate with us tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also the matter at hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. I'll be leaving\Nhim in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still green,\Nbut he's got good intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll be of\Nuse to Detective Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to use this opportunity\Nto make an announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son Hideomi and Hyuga Miyuki-{\i1}san\N{\i0}are engaged to be married!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this true, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I've been having her stay here\Nso she would grow used to the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where is Nobuko-{\i1}ojousama {\i0}going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just the only single person left!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I don't see Hideomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably embarrassed.\NI'll go get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Hattori! Out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real reason you brought us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!\NI just wanted to see ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding! The truth is--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mitsuaki.\NCould you put my father on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's asleep at the moment.\NWe're just about to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find Hideomi anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck did he--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuaki-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right below you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone cut the\Nlights and attacked me with--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0}!\NWhat's going on?! Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideomi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... why would he...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's locked from the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get the master key!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check around\Noutside with the guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0}!\NWhat's going on?! Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective! Here's the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! He used a rope to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where's Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's there. Down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he fell onto the fence...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that the killer is\NMr. Nagato's son, Hideomi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideomi-{\i1}san {\i0}didn't do it!\NThere must be some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still a murderer,\Nwhatever the reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give my Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0} back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hideomi-{\i1}san {\i0}would never do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we don't know\Nhe's the person we saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only saw someone\Nwith bandages on their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandages?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideomi-{\i1}san {\i0}had burn\Nscars all over his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw the killer\Nshortly after 10:00 pm,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when everyone happened\Nto be in the third-story bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everyone" being...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, Heiji, Ran, Conan, Take-{\i1}san\N{\i0}the butler, and Yasue-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do when they left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stayed in the room\Nwith the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think the killer prepared\Nthat grappling hook to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no question\Nthat the killer used it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was still swaying when\Nwe checked around outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where's Hideomi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nowhere to be seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We looked for him while\Nthe police were on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Hideomi-{\i1}san {\i0}is clearly the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:13:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we've found the\Nkiller's weapon, hat, and bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Analysis should prove--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this on his right hand?\NIt's like he was stabbed by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably from the\Nknife or the fence he fell on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Takagi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exterior security cameras show\Nnobody leaving after the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the killer's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...still in the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The president!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Anyone in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the ruckus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see what all\Nthe noise was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you before then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was irritated, so I\Nhad a drink in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. While complaining\Nto a friend on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the alcohol,\Nbut I can't recall who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, is it true that\NHideomi killed Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I figured he would eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two would fight every\Ntime they saw each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seemed to be\Nfriends since childhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they were like cat\Nand dog after the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There was a big fire\Nat a nearby inn twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideomi and Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nhigh-schoolers at the time, passed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuaki-{\i1}san {\i0}tried to stop him,\Nbut Hideomi plunged into the flames
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and rescued a little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyuga Miyuki, to be precise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hence the "bond of flames."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideomi's face was burned as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, he quit school,\Nshut himself in his room,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretended to write novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No women got near him, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She used that to make a pass at him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get recommended as Father's secretary,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even marry into the family!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Nobuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ever since everyone\Nleft the room in an uproar,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though things have been fuzzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything strange\Nhappen afterward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all. Hyuga-{\i1}kun {\i0}stayed\Nwith me until Ran-san arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is no time to look\Nfor your first love now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't. Please forget about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me already!\NWhy'd you bring me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, the president said he\Nheard strange sounds last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange sounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone sprinting through\Nthe hall in the middle of the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and something hitting\Nsomething else, lots of times!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it have been...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Someone inside the house
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was doing something\Nfor tonight's murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and my old man figured it was\Na burglar scoping the place out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we brought in security and called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought he'd show up again tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was a life that was taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A premeditated murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn't it seem strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:17:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Mori Kogoro guy you\Nmade famous was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer musta been really\Nconfident with his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or he couldn't change his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What bothers me are the killer's\Nitems that were lying by the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no need to drop the hat\Nor bandages, never mind the weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the way the killer purposely\Nshowed his face to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost as if to frame Hideomi-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who coulda done that\Nis Nobuko-{\i1}san{\i0}, who left beforehand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We then searched every nook\Nand cranny of the mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Hideomi-{\i1}san {\i0}was nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all about to give\Nup two evenings later, when...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't find him anywhere, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault Hideomi never married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you saying\Nhe held back for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just meant that he\Nthought highly of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop! That pond is deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that pen is my father's\Nkeepsake! Without it, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drain the water, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one filthy pond...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam kept carp in it,\Nbut once she passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why did this have to happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Hideo-{\i1}oniisama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is his estimated time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been dead for\Napproximately 1.5 to 2 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuaki-{\i1}san {\i0}was\Npushed off the veranda
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at 10:00 the night before last,\N44 hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Hideomi-{\i1}san {\i0}drowned himself\Nin this pond before we arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything would fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he didn't drown to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be sure until the autopsy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he likely ingested poison\Nbefore entering the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The body didn't float up because\Nof these rocks in his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Hideomi-{\i1}san {\i0}carried the rocks\Ninto the pond and poisoned himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably didn't want\Nanyone to see him dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, as hostile as Hideomi-{\i1}san {\i0}and\NMitsuaki-{\i1}san {\i0}were with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,murder is a bit much...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible. Hideomi-{\i1}sama {\i0}and\NYasue-{\i1}ojousama {\i0}were very close,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he was vehemently against\Nher marriage with Mitsuaki-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he couldn't stomach the\Nidea of losing his dear little sister
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to his bad friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish child...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure! Here's the lab report!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The marks on the knife match\Nthe wounds on Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0}'s arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the blood on the\Nknife matches his, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hair follicles in the hat and\Nbandages belong to Hideomi-{\i1}san{\i0}."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, there was\Na meter-long grappling hook
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0}'s jacket pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A grappling hook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the cut on his right\Nhand from the knife, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was different...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the blood type\Nof the saliva on the knife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't any.\NSeems it was wiped off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! I found this\Npaper in his pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm not fit to marry you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose death to atone\Nfor the sin I committed."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is his will! Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}!\NIt's addressed to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Hideomi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s handwriting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it looks like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get some of his\Nwritings from his room...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}! Here's\Nthe pen you dropped in...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideomi-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This pen's really been burnt...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This case is totally weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even more unnatural is that will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It said, "The sin I committed."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning he wrote it after the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't have time to write a will then!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means someone\Nforged it or forced him to write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, there's little\Ndoubt that someone drowned him
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the will after poisoning him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the only time\Nanyone got near the pond
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was when we all went looking for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Hideomi-{\i1}san {\i0}had\Nbeen murdered before it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't tell me\NHideomi-{\i1}san {\i0}was actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! His estimated\Ntime of death was...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there was a way, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Hattori...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever killed someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.10,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.61,0:24:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Case of the Eminent Family's\NStrange Deaths, Part 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.10,0:24:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.55,0:24:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foutain pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.46,0:24:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.39,0:24:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Solved, solved, solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.13,0:24:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The case is solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.81,0:24:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
